Simcorp Developer (Simcorp, Development, configuration, upgrade
Simcorp Developer (Simcorp, Development, configuration, upgrade
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
Salary:  GBP500 - GBP650 per day + expensesSimcorp Developer (Simcorp, Development, configuration, upgrade, asset classes)
Global consultancy is looking for a Simcorp Developer to work onsite for one of their clients onsite at their head office in Abu Dhabi. The Simcorp Developer will working on the hands on development of Simcorp Dimension.
The Simcorp Developer will be responsible for the configuration and upgrade across multiple asset classes. The role of the Simcorp Developer will involve liaising with the business users and stakeholders to understand their needs, meaning a good functional understanding of Simcorp is essential.
The suitable candidate will have come from a proven Simcorp Development background. In depth knowledge of Simcorp, Development, configuration, upgrade, asset classes is key. Excellent interpersonal and communication skills is essential.
